          <li>Gullfoss Waterfall's raw power as thousands of gallons of water crash over the edge every second.</li>
          <li>Hiking through colorful geothermal landscapes and soaking in the naturally warm waters of Reykjadalur Hot Spring River.</li>
          <li>Walking between North American and Eurasian tectonic plates at √ûingvellir, one of the few places on Earth where this continental divide is visible above ground.</li>
        </ul>
